  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EngineNarrationStep
  stepLabel: INTRODUCTION
  narrationText: "Welcome. Today, we're going to discover how a 6-cylinder engine
    works \u2014 from the very first part to the moment power leaves the system.\n\nThis
    engine is inspired by the LEGO Technic Porsche 911 RSR \u2014 a brilliant mechanical
    model that mirrors a real boxer engine.\n\nWatch closely. Every part has a purpose.
    Let's begin."
